nhc_headline: ...NARDA COULD RESTRENGTHEN TO A CATEGORY 2 HURRICANE SOON...
summary: ...NARDA COULD RESTRENGTHEN TO A CATEGORY 2 HURRICANE SOON... As of 8:00 AM PDT Thu Sep 25 the center of Narda was located near 16.1, -116.6 with movement WNW at 15 mph. The minimum central pressure was 980 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 90 mph.
